Getting Started

Let's follow a learning-by-doing approach. As a warm-up, let's first estimate parameters in serial. In a second step, we use several workers on a cluster.

Example in serial

using MSM
using Plots

x = collect(range(-3.14, 4.0, length = 10))
y = sin.(x)
p = plot(x, y)

Example in parallel

using MSM
using Plots

x = collect(range(-3.14, 4.0, length = 10))
y = cos.(x)
p = plot(x, y)
